title: Proto Black Watch Face 360
summary: a black or white robot styled watchface with a second meter on the left

descriptionHTML:
This cool black or white prototype watch face will enhance your smartwatch experience.

Seconds are counted on this black or white watch face via a meter on the left hand side.

The battery is displayed on the triangular metal module near the center.

The date is displayed in the Month / Day / Year format

Time is in 12 hour mode, with a 24 hour option accessible in the settings screen on the device.

This black watch face is designed for the moto 360 and sony smartwatch 3 and will function on other watches.
